snippet.title: Neurovoider - Release trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/400450

NeuroVoider is a twin-stick shooter with a pinch of rogue-lite. Play alone or with up to 4 friends for a total rampage and tons of loot.

http://neurovoider.com/

Soundtrack by Dan Terminus (courtesy of Blood Music), check it out on: https://blood-music.bandcamp.com/album/the-wrath-of-code
